<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Open the door to OpenRoaming!</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#080D4A]">
<div class="container mx-auto px-8 pb-8 pt-[50px]">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-[18px] p-6 shadow-md">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Forgot Password Request - OpenRoaming Portal</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
            To confirm your password account reset request,
            please use this one to perform the verification: <strong>{{ currentPassword }}</strong></p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg"> And click
            <a class="font-bold text-[#7BBA29] underline"
               href="{{ absolute_url('/login/link') ~ '?' ~ 'uuid=' ~ uuid|url_encode ~ '&verificationCode=' ~ verificationCode }}">here!</a>
        </p>
        <p class="class= mt-2 text-lg">
            To be able to confirm your password, you have to log in and insert a new one.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
